title: The Top Five Movies of 2020
description:
This has been a strange year for movies, most of which were seen at home. But we didn't struggle to find some that lit up our imagination and reflected the times. Sean and Amanda are joined by Chris Ryan and Adam Nayman to pick their top five films of 2020.

Hosts: Sean Fennessey and Amanda Dobbins
Guests: Chris Ryan and Adam Nayman
